{"tid":484829,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"點解無女人強姦男人","createTime":"2017-11-30T12:02:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-09T01:48:00.000Z","uid":389,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"c42f88448619d3796b67f41882ae01a3c169e1bc","tid":484829,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T12:02:53.000Z","msg":"點解香港法律無女人強姦男人？<br />\n只有男人強姦女人同女人強姦女人？"},{"pid":"f640ad6022ac3a304b740c15e333e0fc73b72411","tid":484829,"uid":94828,"like":45,"dislike":1,"score":44,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T12:03:35.000Z","msg":"有 不過被人告既都係男人"},{"pid":"d1bb19f10fc17efa293c91f939ba580999ddb916","tid":484829,"uid":389,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T12:04:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有 不過被人告既都係男人</blockquote><br />\n我指既係法例上<br />\n只有女人可以被強姦"},{"pid":"5b146e38daefd4910fbedb7d6841943efa0588a2","tid":484829,"uid":31887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T12:04:38.000Z","msg":"女人姦男人一樣男人坐監<br />\n你唔扯旗咪唔犯法"},{"pid":"b57f8b51b192854acf9afe6687c2183e5a733397","tid":484829,"uid":22360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T12:04:51.000Z","msg":"強姦 X<br />\n強制性插入行為 O"},{"pid":"da8d95aa1c3036f608145fe985bd7f38a38c94d5","tid":484829,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T12:05:52.000Z","msg":"罪行元素<br />\n<br />\n強姦是指男子在女子不同意之下與她性交。《刑事罪行條例》（香港法例第200章）第118(3)條列明，如任何男子： <br />\n「(a)與一名女子非法性交，而性交時該女子對此並不同意；及(b)當時他知道該女子並不同意性交，或罔顧該女子是否對此同意」，便干犯強姦罪，最高刑罰是終身監禁。<br />\n<br />\n在香港，只有男性會干犯強姦罪，受害人必須是女性。如一名男子與一名女子非法性交，該名女子當時並不同意性交，而男子當時知道她不同意性交，或沒有理會她是否同意性交，他便干犯強姦罪。任何女子協助或唆使一名男子強姦另一名女子，可能會被控協助及教唆強姦。<br />\n<br />\n根據普通法，法庭會立論假設14歲以下的男童無能力性交。不過，《刑事罪行條例》 第118O條已廢除未滿14歲男童無能力性交、肛交或獸交的法律推定。 因此，年滿10歲（開始需要負上刑事責任的年齡）至未滿14歲的男童亦要就涉及性交的罪行，負上刑事責任。<br />\n<br />\n至於10歲至14歲的被告，法庭會考慮多一個法律原理，稱為「無犯罪能力推斷」；即控方必須在毫無合理疑點之下，證明被告知道自己的所作所為並非純粹因為頑皮，他知道有關行為是嚴重錯誤。"},{"pid":"786fe0aa340515ab24e9bbf6d771a0f9a401dd44","tid":484829,"uid":53911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T12:07:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rape_in_English_law\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.m.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FRape_in_English_law&d=vzobyLwFp2vGH3L1F%2B0ji5zN29kXmk9bB7xBuKM86BA%3D&h=46275cdd\" target=\"_blank\">https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rape_in_English_law</a><br />\n<br />\n睇下英格蘭法律對rape 嘅定義"},{"pid":"2dcb5218c1b47feffa567a20236d75ccea9ce908","tid":484829,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T12:07:16.000Z","msg":"其實之所以得女人係強姦案受害<br />\n因為香港法律並無「強姦男人」呢項<br />\n<br />\n得「雞姦」"},{"pid":"e58079e753488de313a51ead008289515eb3b3dc","tid":484829,"uid":106614,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T12:09:49.000Z","msg":"小心比女權咬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b0ac53c66b54f9f39cadebeac4ad296228cedd1","tid":484829,"uid":389,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T12:10:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>小心比女權咬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n女權其中一個論據就係<br />\n<br />\n只有女人可以被人強姦"},{"pid":"68266e67d32ceb414adedf9c3540e144cce07b2d","tid":484829,"uid":19978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T12:11:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>小心比女權咬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n女權其中一個論據就係<br />\n<br />\n只有女人可以被人強姦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n真心咩"},{"pid":"7796ef6d42b416a39de13e878ae8b705fdde3355","tid":484829,"uid":7078,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T12:13:13.000Z","msg":"因為法律強姦緊男人"},{"pid":"82ce85b63b001802dfa753b2a8e03275ec50b44f","tid":484829,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T12:15:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>小心比女權咬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n女權其中一個論據就係<br />\n<